CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: Marti Technologies Inc. operates a mobility app that provides multiple transportation services to its riders. It offers a ride hailing service that matches riders with drivers traveling in the same direction and operates a fleet of e-mopeds, e-bikes, and e-scooters. The company was founded in 2018 and is based in Dover, Delaware.
